shiftCdrTab
Class OfficerAssignment

java.lang.Object
  shiftCdrTab.OfficerAssignment

public class OfficerAssignment
extends java.lang.Object

The OfficerAssignment class represents a single officer's assigned tasks for a particular shift. These are set by the Shift Commander at the beginning of each shift during roll call and reviewed, edited for any changes, and finalized on the Shift Commander Summary Report at the end of the shift. A list of OfficerAssignments comprises the assignments list for a particular shift. There is exactly one assignments list in every ShiftCdrReport. The list and the OfficerAssignments comprising the list are unique to the shift that the ShiftCdrReport represents. The permissions attached to an OfficerAssignment are as follows: Officers - can view only their own past and present OfficerAssignments Shift Commanders - can view all OfficerAssignments, but can edit only those which they have created Supervisor - can view and edit all OfficerAssignments
